  ('real-estate-moex-01226', 'real-estate', 'real-estate-moex-106-ce711c8d', 'sub-real-estate-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '依不動產估價技術規則第 7 條規定：「依本規則辦理估價所稱之面積，已辦理登記者，以登記之面積為 準」但未辦理登記或以部分面積為估價者，應如何處理？ 省略不處理  先探求未登記之原因  當作無價值  調查註明', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5605d540739a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5609be6868db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "601", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "不動產估價概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 3, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "brokers", "db_exam_id": "real-estate"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-moex-01227', 'real-estate', 'real-estate-moex-106-ce711c8d', 'sub-real-estate-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '如您於捷運地下街承租營運中，隔壁店家因故不與捷運局續租，此時您打算一併承租擴大經營，所承租 之租金屬性應屬下列何者？ 市場租金  正常租金  經濟租金  限定租金', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5605d540739a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5609be6868db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "601", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "不動產估價概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 4, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "brokers", "db_exam_id": "real-estate"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-moex-01228', 'real-estate', 'real-estate-moex-106-ce711c8d', 'sub-real-estate-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '臺北市政府最近發布之10月份住宅價格指數，中山松山南港區標準住宅總價1,224萬元、萬華文山北投 區1,080萬元，其價差達144萬元。以上的價差分析，屬下列何種運用？ 定率法  比率法  定額法  差額法', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5605d540739a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5609be6868db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "601", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "不動產估價概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 5, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "brokers", "db_exam_id": "real-estate"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-moex-01229', 'real-estate', 'real-estate-moex-106-ce711c8d', 'sub-real-estate-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '某出租型不動產之年總收益為100萬元，若總費用率為總收益的40%，收益資本化率4%，則該不動產之 收益價格應為多少？ 1,000萬元  1,200萬元  1,500萬元  2,500萬元', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5605d540739a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5609be6868db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "601", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "不動產估價概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "brokers", "db_exam_id": "real-estate"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-moex-01230', 'real-estate', 'real-estate-moex-106-ce711c8d', 'sub-real-estate-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '不動產估價比較法就「畸零地或有合併使用之交易」所進行之調整，是屬於何項調整？ 情況調整  價格日期調整  區域因素調整  個別因素調整', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5605d540739a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5609be6868db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "601", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "不動產估價概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "brokers", "db_exam_id": "real-estate"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('real-estate-moex-01231', 'real-estate', 'real-estate-moex-106-ce711c8d', 'sub-real-estate-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '關於不動產估價收益法之總費用估算項目，下列何者正確？ 只能算地價稅，如地上權地租不能算  房屋稅只適用於保存登記之建物 所得稅亦應計算    維修費、保險費亦應計算', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T07:10:08+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5605d540739a", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5609be6868db", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "106180", "c": "601", "s": "1102", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "不動產估價概要", "year": "106", "exam_name": "106年專門職業及技術人員高等考試建築師、技師、第二次食品技師考試暨普通考試不動產經紀人、記帳士考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "brokers", "db_exam_id": "real-estate"}'::jsonb, NULL)
